Recipe to make tea.
Step1: Boil water
Step2: Warm up teapot.
Step3: Put tea into teapot and add water.
Step4: Cover teapot and cover Steep tea.
Step5: Strain tea solids and pour hot tea into tea cups.
Step6: ADD milk and sugar 
Step7: Heat and stir well for some time.
Step8: Use tea Stainer to filter the tea.
step9: Drink tea.

